- When not scrolled: `bg-transparent` (so the hero image shows through on the home page)

**Mobile Drawer:**
- Add the "Collections" link here too
- Add the brand name "Lumière" at the top of the drawer in large Playfair Display gold text
- Add social icons (Instagram, Twitter, Facebook) at the bottom of the drawer (import from lucide-react)

